Description: Return from Egypt, with the holy Family on a boat guided by angels; after Lodovico Carracci; plate 12 from Jameson's 'Collection of Pictures by W. G. Coesvelt, Esq of London' (London, 1836). c.1836 Etching on chine collé
Curator's comments: From 'Collection of Pictures by W. G. Coesvelt, Esq of London', see 1865,0610.666. For painting see Brogi, 'Ludovico Carracci (1555-1619)', Bologna, 2001, cat. No.66.
Subjects: return of the holy family from egypt
Associated titles: Collection of Pictures by W. G. Coesvelt, Esq of London
